description:
Newly renovated 1 bedroom apartment. It includes a fully equipped kitchen, clean and functional bathroom, a cozy queen size bed and a natural well lit living room with top notch Tv and Bose sound system. Located in a friendly neighborhood with bars, restaurants, banks, pharmacies and a 24/7 supermarket steps away. Parking space around the house and 7min walk to the train, 20 min train ride to Manhattan.
